---
layout: base-it.njk
title: Galleria & Aggiornamenti
description: Foto, momenti di vita quotidiana e aggiornamenti sul nostro Alaskan Malamute.
permalink: /it/galleria/
---

<section class="cat-hero">
  <div class="container cat-hero-inner">
    <p class="cat-hero-eyebrow">It's A Malamute</p>
    <h1 class="cat-hero-title">Galleria & Aggiornamenti</h1>
    <p class="cat-hero-desc">Foto, momenti di vita quotidiana e aggiornamenti sul nostro Alaskan Malamute.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container breadcrumb-inner">
    <a href="/it/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
    <span>Galleria</span>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="cat-posts-section">
  <div class="container">
    {% set galleryPosts = collections.it_galleria %}
    {% if galleryPosts and galleryPosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      {% for post in galleryPosts | reverse %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="gallery-item">
        {% if post.data.cover %}
          <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
        {% else %}
          <div class="gallery-item-placeholder">🐾</div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay">
          <span class="gallery-item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div style="text-align:center; padding: 80px 0; color: var(--text-light);">
      <p style="font-family: var(--ff-mono); font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;">Prossimamente</p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--arctic);">Le prime foto sono in arrivo.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:12px; font-size:0.95rem;">Torna presto per scoprire la galleria.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
